<p><strong>Kingdom of Stone:</strong> A Monolithic Species</p>
<p>An abandoned tale series that will be picked up again some day</p>
<p><strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/andarielhalo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1750255); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1750255&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721492" alt="AndarielHalo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1750255)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/andarielhalo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1750255); return false;">AndarielHalo</a></span></p>
<p>Eat more of my SCPs. <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/andariel-halo-file" target="_blank">Eat them all.</a></p>
<p>Also please eat some of these</p>
<ul>
