<li><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/manna-charitable-foundation-hub">Manna Charitable Foundation 2000</a></strong> The sequel to the above, collaborationed with <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-reach" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1779895); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1779895&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721492" alt="Dr Reach" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1779895)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-reach" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1779895); return false;">Dr Reach</a></span></li>
<li><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/the-stuff-industry-hub">The Stuff Industry</a></strong> What happens when everyone around you at work is a complete idiot and so are you, but not only does no one get fired, but you actually turn a profit? I don't know, some stuff.</li>
